" /> <br />\n過埋隔離村睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等睇包膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打講下都曬鹽差幾遠</blockquote><br />\n我屋企鹽都冇 唯一希望黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc7d1ca8d1ecda3e986cc6bc3514e88571f6bfe","tid":223744,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ1OrFF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ1OrFF.jpg&h=717a8b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有鳩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  承為35蚊"},{"pid":"8f65ae86e689880abf98f5bb972a8b44dd93b2e5","tid":223744,"uid":95908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用呢隻啦，整落去嗰陣痛到仆街，但之後就會麻痹左，可以食到嘢仲好快好得返<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0e8bzylq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0e8bzylq&h=0711cd0b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但搽落去嗰下你真係會眼淚口水都流哂出嚟，過左一陣就冇嘢，其實真係恩物，搽左之後就好似你粒飛滋冇左咁</blockquote><br />\n上次用過一次 搽果下真係痛到升天<br />\n之後個傷口白曬 然後點搞點hi都唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72adcd74f365409a653a1d1b568dac4b1fbfc5d","tid":223744,"uid":59884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"我平時會用麥盧卡蜂蜜乸乸佢, 第日即好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a06b554eb4d7b77b6c1cf702299a7d3b403a3d6","tid":223744,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/001839_ce3bce1c22edc81c6b30b9a2f999230f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F001839_ce3bce1c22edc81c6b30b9a2f999230f.jpg&h=54754681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩上網睇師奶王國話對唔準粒野就會搞到爛牙肉<br />\n再加上佢依句野真係搞到我有d手震<br />\n<br />\n佢張野話印乾左粒飛滋會發揮得好d<br />\n咁就首先用第二枝棉花棒吸一吸先<br />\n依下已經好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v356Wm5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv356Wm5.jpg&h=8a3cab5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n送枝棉花棒 再加pat gel<br />\n<br />\n對落去個5秒痛撚到呢<br />\n<br />\nlong完口 好似冇咁痛<br />\n<br />\n過多陣 奶都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/002522_a89ffa333fe35188341b9db88345fc21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F002522_a89ffa333fe35188341b9db88345fc21.jpg&h=77177282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過咁就35蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食到餐飯架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nps.大間d既7仔先有 細間冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}